title: [Grawood Farmstead, Maze]
description: Towering stalks of corn wrapped in thick green leaves sway overhead in the slight breeze.  Thin yellow ribbons fly from the tops of a few of  the stalks, waving like proud banners.  The wind gusts gently, pulling at the yellow silken threads attached to the corn husks.
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
